    <title></title>
    <url>/2022/04/15/Intro.SQL/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Intro-to-SQL"><a href="#Intro-to-SQL" class="headerlink" title="Intro. to SQL"></a>Intro. to SQL</h1><h1 id="Foremost"><a href="#Foremost" class="headerlink" title="Foremost"></a>Foremost</h1><h2 id="一、SQL-语句的执行顺序"><a href="#一、SQL-语句的执行顺序" class="headerlink" title="一、SQL 语句的执行顺序"></a>一、SQL 语句的执行顺序</h2><p>对于 SQL，有以下基本语句：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">DISTINCT</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>select_list<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>left_table<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="operator">&lt;</span>join_type<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="keyword">JOIN</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>right_table<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ON</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>join_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WHERE</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>where_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>group_by_list<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">HAVING</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>having_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>order_by_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">LIMIT <span class="operator">&lt;</span>limit_number<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>从逻辑和应用上我们可以得到如下执行顺序：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="number">7</span>) <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="comment">/* 处理SELECT列表，产生 VT7 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">8</span>) <span class="keyword">DISTINCT</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>select_list<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/* 将重复的行从 VT7 中删除，产品 VT8 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">1</span>) <span class="keyword">FROM</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>left_table<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/* 对FROM子句中的表执行笛卡尔积(交叉联接)，生成虚拟表 VT1。 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">3</span>) <span class="operator">&lt;</span>join_type<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="keyword">JOIN</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>right_table<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/* 如果指定了OUTER JOIN(相对于CROSS JOIN或INNER JOIN)，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">保留表中未找到匹配的行将作为外部行添加到 VT2，生成 VT3。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">如果FROM子句包含两个以上的表，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">则对上一个联接生成的结果表和下一个表重复执行步骤1到步骤3，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">直到处理完所有的表位置。 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">2</span>) <span class="keyword">ON</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>join_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span><span class="comment">/* 对 VT1 应用 ON 筛选器，只有那些使为真才被插入到 VT2。 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">4</span>) <span class="keyword">WHERE</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>where_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span><span class="comment">/* 对 VT3 应用 WHERE 筛选器，只有使为true的行才插入VT4。 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">5</span>) <span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>group_by_list<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/* 按 GROUP BY子句中的列列表对 VT4 中的行进行分组，生成 VT5 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">6</span>) <span class="keyword">HAVING</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>having_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/* 对 VT5 应用 HAVING 筛选器，只有使为true的组插入到 VT6 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">9</span>) <span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>order_by_condition<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/* 将 VT8 中的行按 ORDER BY子句中的列列表顺序，生成一个游标(VC10)，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">生成表TV11，并返回给调用者。 */</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="number">10</span>)LIMIT <span class="operator">&lt;</span>limit_number<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/*LIMIT 控制显示的元组数*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>即按顺序排列为：</p>
<ul>
<li>FROM：对 FROM 语句中的所有<strong>子表</strong>先<strong>做笛卡尔积</strong>，生成表 VT1（不管是普通的笛卡尔积，还是其它各种类型的连接，都需要先做笛卡尔积）</li>
<li>ON：对 VT1 按条件筛选<strong>行</strong>，只有为真时被插入到 VT2</li>
<li>JOIN：根据 JOIN 类型，如果指定了 OUTER JOIN（相对于CROSS JOIN或INNER JOIN），<strong>保留表中未找到匹配的行将作为外部行添加到 VT2，生成 VT3</strong></li>
<li>WHERE：对 VT1 按条件筛选<strong>行</strong>，只有为真时被插入到 VT4</li>
<li>GROUP BY：对 VT4 中的元组进行分组，生成 VT5</li>
<li>HAVING：对 VT5 按条件筛选<strong>组</strong>，只有为真时被插入到 VT6</li>
<li>SELECT：处理表，只插入选中的<strong>列</strong>到 VT7</li>
<li>DISTINCT：将重复的<strong>行</strong>从表中删除，产生 VT8</li>
<li>ORDER BY：对 VT8 中的<strong>行</strong>按条件排序，产生 VT9</li>
<li>LIMIT：保留限制的<strong>行</strong>数，生成 VT10，呈现给调用者</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="二、语句功能速记"><a href="#二、语句功能速记" class="headerlink" title="二、语句功能速记"></a>二、语句功能速记</h2><p>记住语句功能最重要的是记住语句的<strong>输入值</strong>和<strong>返回值</strong>的<strong>类型</strong>和<strong>格式</strong> </p>
<h1 id="Specification"><a href="#Specification" class="headerlink" title="Specification"></a>Specification</h1><h2 id="3-5-集合运算"><a href="#3-5-集合运算" class="headerlink" title="3.5 集合运算"></a>3.5 集合运算</h2><p>集合运算 <strong>union, intersect, except</strong> 分别对应关系代数中的 $A\cup B,A\cap B,A-B$，由于是集合运算，默认情况下会将运算结果中重复的元组自动去除，若想保留重复元组则需要使用 <strong>union all, intersect all, except all</strong> </p>
<p>集合运算的<strong>输入为两个关系</strong> $R_{1,2}$，<strong>输出为一个关系</strong> $R_{new}$，两个关系的属性必须完全相同，否则会出错</p>
<h3 id="3-5-1-并运算"><a href="#3-5-1-并运算" class="headerlink" title="3.5.1 并运算"></a>3.5.1 并运算</h3><p><strong>union</strong> 和 <strong>union all</strong></p>
<p>考虑查询“在 2017 年秋季<strong>或</strong>在 2018 年春季开设的课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Fall&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">union</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Spring&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2018</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-5-2-交运算"><a href="#3-5-2-交运算" class="headerlink" title="3.5.2 交运算"></a>3.5.2 交运算</h3><p><strong>intersect</strong> 和 <strong>intersect all</strong> </p>
<p>考虑查询“既在 2017 年秋季<strong>又</strong>在 2018 年春季开设的课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Fall&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">intersect</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Spring&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2018</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-5-3-差运算"><a href="#3-5-3-差运算" class="headerlink" title="3.5.3 差运算"></a>3.5.3 差运算</h3><p><strong>except</strong> 和 <strong>except all</strong> <span id="except"></span> </p>
<p>差运算对应于关系代数中的差集运算，即 $A-B=A\cap\overline{B}$</p>
<p>考虑查询“既在 2017 年秋季又<strong>不</strong>在 2018 年春季开设的课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Fall&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">except</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Spring&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2018</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-6-空值"><a href="#3-6-空值" class="headerlink" title="3.6 空值"></a>3.6 空值</h2><h3 id="3-6-1-运算"><a href="#3-6-1-运算" class="headerlink" title="3.6.1 运算"></a>3.6.1 运算</h3><ul>
<li><p>对于算术表达式来说，如：$+,-,×,÷$ 等，遇上 <strong>null</strong> 值则结果也是 <strong>null</strong></p>
</li>
<li><p>对于逻辑表达式来说较为复杂：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>and</strong>：true <strong>and</strong> unknown = unknown，false <strong>and</strong> unknown = false，unknown <strong>and</strong> unknown = unknown</li>
<li><strong>or</strong>：true <strong>and</strong> unknown = true，false <strong>and</strong> unknown = unknown，unknown <strong>and</strong> unknown = unknown</li>
<li><strong>not</strong>：<strong>not</strong> unknown = unknown</li>
</ul>
<p>若 <strong>where</strong> 子句谓词对一个元组计算出 <strong>false</strong> 或 <strong>unknown</strong>，则该元组不能被加入结果中</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="3-6-2-空值测试"><a href="#3-6-2-空值测试" class="headerlink" title="3.6.2 空值测试"></a>3.6.2 空值测试</h3><p><strong>is null, is not null</strong> 用于判断一个值是否是空值</p>
<p>考虑查询“$salary$ 为空值的教师”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> name</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> salary <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>is unknown, is not unknown</strong> 用于判断一个逻辑表达式结果是否为 unknown</p>
<h2 id="3-7-聚集函数"><a href="#3-7-聚集函数" class="headerlink" title="3.7 聚集函数"></a>3.7 聚集函数</h2><p>聚集函数（$\text{aggregate function}$）是以值集（集合或多重集合）为输入并返回单个值的函数，SQL 提供了五个标准的固有聚集函数：</p>
<ul>
<li>平均值：<strong>avg</strong></li>
<li>最小值：<strong>min</strong></li>
<li>最大值：<strong>max</strong></li>
<li>总和：<strong>sum</strong> </li>
<li>计数：<strong>count</strong> </li>
</ul>
<h3 id="3-7-1-基本聚集"><a href="#3-7-1-基本聚集" class="headerlink" title="3.7.1 基本聚集"></a>3.7.1 基本聚集</h3><h4 id="1-基本操作"><a href="#1-基本操作" class="headerlink" title="1. 基本操作"></a>1. 基本操作</h4><p>“找出计算机系教师的平均工资”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">avg</span> (salary)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> dept name <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Comp. Sci.&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="2-更名操作"><a href="#2-更名操作" class="headerlink" title="2. 更名操作"></a>2. 更名操作</h4><p>使用完 <strong>avg</strong> 函数后得到的单值会被放在名为 <strong>avg</strong> 的列下方（聚集函数都是此规则），可以对聚集函数进行更名操作，其实质是对名为 <strong>avg</strong> 的列进行更名</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">avg</span> (salary) <span class="keyword">as</span> avg_salary</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> dept name <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Comp. Sci.&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="3-去重操作"><a href="#3-去重操作" class="headerlink" title="3. 去重操作"></a>3. 去重操作</h4><p>假设要“找出在 2018 春季学期授课的教师总数”，此时有可能出现一位教师同时在一个学期开多门课的情况，而他只应该被计算一次，可以使用 <strong>distinct</strong> 去重：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">count</span> (<span class="keyword">distinct</span> ID)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> teaches</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Spring&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2018</span>;<span class="number">0</span>O1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>若要使用 <strong>count</strong> 计算元组数量，可以</p>
<ul>
<li>使用 $*$ 作为 <strong>count</strong> 的输入</li>
<li>使用 <strong>主码</strong> 作为 <strong>count</strong> 的输入</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">count</span> (<span class="operator">*</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> course;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-7-2-分组聚集（group-by）"><a href="#3-7-2-分组聚集（group-by）" class="headerlink" title="3.7.2 分组聚集（group by）"></a>3.7.2 分组聚集（group by）</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">GROUP</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>group_by_list<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>group by</strong> 子句中给出的<strong>一个或多个属性</strong>被用来构造分组，在分组子句中所有属性上取值相同的元组将被分在一个组内，<strong>每个分组只被允许输出一个元组</strong> </p>
<p>考虑查询“找出每个系的平均工资”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> dept name, <span class="built_in">avg</span> (salary) <span class="keyword">as</span> avg_salary</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> dept_name;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>而对于缺省 <strong>group by</strong> 的查询语句则<strong>视关系中的每个元组为一个分组</strong></p>
<p>==当使用分组语句时，很重要的点在于确保出现在 <strong>select</strong> 语句中而没有被聚集的属性只能是出现在 <strong>group by</strong> 子句中的那些属性==</p>
<p>这是因为 <strong>select</strong> 会将 VT6 选中的列插入新表 VT7 中，可以看出由 VT6→VT7 的过程使表 VT6 中的每个分组在 VT7 中只表现出一个元组，也就是说将分组转换成元组是在这一步发生的。当 <strong>select</strong> 中为聚集函数或 <strong>group by</strong> 子句属性时，它们要么只有一条要么整个分组的值相同，因此可以在一个元组中表示出来；而其余属性由于分组中每个元组的值都不同，显然无法在一个元组中表现，因此出错</p>
<img src="D:\总文档\Markdown\MD杂项\MD.IMG\image-20220312103549988.png" alt="image-20220312103549988" style="zoom: 80%;" />

<center>VT6（此处与 VT5 相同）</center>

<img src="D:\总文档\Markdown\MD杂项\MD.IMG\image-20220312103714191.png" alt="image-20220312103714191" style="zoom: 80%;" />

<center>VT7</center>

<h3 id="3-7-3-having-子句"><a href="#3-7-3-having-子句" class="headerlink" title="3.7.3 having 子句"></a>3.7.3 having 子句</h3><p><strong>having</strong> 子句针对 <strong>group by</strong> 子句构成的每个分组进行筛选，与 <strong>select</strong> 子句情况类似，它是对整个分组共有属性进行筛选，任何出现在 <strong>having</strong> 子句中而没有被聚集的属性必须出现在 <strong>group by</strong> 子句中 <span id="having"></span></p>
<p>考虑查询“找出平均工资超过 42000 美元的那些系的教师的平均工资”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> dept name, <span class="built_in">avg</span> (salary) <span class="keyword">as</span> avg salary</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> dept name</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">having</span> <span class="built_in">avg</span> (salary) <span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="number">42000</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-7-4-对空值和布尔值的聚集"><a href="#3-7-4-对空值和布尔值的聚集" class="headerlink" title="3.7.4 对空值和布尔值的聚集"></a>3.7.4 对空值和布尔值的聚集</h3><h4 id="1-空值"><a href="#1-空值" class="headerlink" title="1. 空值"></a>1. 空值</h4><ul>
<li>除了 <strong>count</strong>(*) 之外的所有聚集函数都忽略输入集合的空值</li>
<li>如果输入集合中不存在非空值：<ul>
<li><strong>count</strong> 返回 $0$</li>
<li>其它聚集函数返回 $\text{null}$ </li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="2-布尔值"><a href="#2-布尔值" class="headerlink" title="2. 布尔值"></a>2. 布尔值</h4><p>对于布尔值，SQL 有专门的聚集函数对其进行处理：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>some</strong>，对输入集合进行<strong>或</strong>（$or$）运算</li>
<li><strong>every</strong>，对输入集合进行<strong>与</strong>（$and$）运算</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="3-8-嵌套子查询"><a href="#3-8-嵌套子查询" class="headerlink" title="3.8 嵌套子查询"></a>3.8 嵌套子查询</h2><h3 id="3-8-1-集合成员资格（in）"><a href="#3-8-1-集合成员资格（in）" class="headerlink" title="3.8.1 集合成员资格（in）"></a>3.8.1 集合成员资格（in）</h3><p><strong>in</strong> 和 <strong>not in</strong> 用于 <strong>where</strong> 子句中，<strong>返回的是布尔值</strong>，形式为 </p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>A1,A2,...<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>R<span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">/*A:attribute 为表中的属性</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">R:relation 可以是一个嵌套的子查询也可以是一个已存在的关系，但这个关系中的属性必须要和&lt;A1,A2,...&gt;中的属性一一对应*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>用于判断一个元组中的属性集 $&lt;A_1,A_2,\cdots&gt;$ 是否在 $R$ 中有对应属性值与之完全相同的元组</p>
<h4 id="1-关系集合（单属性）"><a href="#1-关系集合（单属性）" class="headerlink" title="1. 关系集合（单属性）"></a>1. 关系集合（单属性）</h4><p>考虑查询“既在 2017 年秋季又在 2018 年春季开设的课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="keyword">distinct</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Fall&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span> <span class="keyword">and</span></span><br><span class="line">      course_id <span class="keyword">in</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Spring&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2018</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>意为：先对 $section$ 查询在 2018 年春季开设的 $course_id$，这些 $course_id$ 组成一个子关系 $R’$，之后筛选出 $section$ 中存在于 $R’$ 的 $course_id$，再与在 2017 年秋季开课的 $course_id$ 相与即得到所需要的查询</p>
<p>考虑查询“既在 2017 年秋季又<strong>不</strong>在 2018 年春季开设的课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="keyword">distinct</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Fall&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span> <span class="keyword">and</span></span><br><span class="line">      course_id <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> section</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Spring&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2018</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>作为与<a href="#except">前面</a>达到相同功能的 <strong>except</strong> 子句作为对比</p>
<h4 id="2-枚举集合"><a href="#2-枚举集合" class="headerlink" title="2. 枚举集合"></a>2. 枚举集合</h4><p><strong>in</strong> 和 <strong>not in</strong> 也可以用于枚举集合，下面查询为：“找出既不叫“Mozart”也不叫“Einstein””的教师的姓名</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="keyword">distinct</span> name</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> name <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> (<span class="string">&#x27;Mozart&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Einstein&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="3-关系集合（多属性）"><a href="#3-关系集合（多属性）" class="headerlink" title="3. 关系集合（多属性）"></a>3. 关系集合（多属性）</h4><p>考虑查询“找出选修了 $ID$ 为 $10101$ 的教师讲授的课程段的（不同）学生的总数”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">count</span> (<span class="keyword">distinct</span> ID)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> takes</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> (course_id, sec id, semester, <span class="keyword">year</span>) <span class="keyword">in</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> course_id, sec id, semester, <span class="keyword">year</span></span><br><span class="line">                                              <span class="keyword">from</span> teaches</span><br><span class="line">                                              <span class="keyword">where</span> teaches.ID<span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;10101&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>但有的 SQL 不支持上述操作</strong> </p>
<h3 id="3-8-2-集合比较（some）"><a href="#3-8-2-集合比较（some）" class="headerlink" title="3.8.2 集合比较（some）"></a>3.8.2 集合比较（some）</h3><h3 id="3-8-3-空关系测试（exists）"><a href="#3-8-3-空关系测试（exists）" class="headerlink" title="3.8.3 空关系测试（exists）"></a>3.8.3 空关系测试（exists）</h3><p><strong>exists</strong> 和 <strong>not exists</strong> 用于判断一个子查询的结果中是否存在元组。<strong>exists</strong> 在其子句中的子查询非空时返回 <strong>true</strong> </p>
<p>考虑查询“找出 $2017$ 秋季学期和  $2018$ 春季学期都开课的课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> section <span class="keyword">as</span> S</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Fall&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span> <span class="keyword">and</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">exists</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span></span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">from</span> section <span class="keyword">as</span> T</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">where</span> semester <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Spring&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> <span class="keyword">year</span><span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2018</span> <span class="keyword">and</span></span><br><span class="line">              S.course_id<span class="operator">=</span> T.course_id);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>此处查询说明了 SQL 的一个特性：来自外层查询的相关名称（上述查询中的 $S$）可以用在 <strong>where</strong> 子句的子查询中，这种子查询称为 <strong>相关子查询</strong>。该查询的执行过程为父查询 $1$ 个值，子查询对这个得到的值进行 $1$ 轮查询，总查询次数是 $mn$；而 <strong>非相关子查询</strong> 不需要把父查询的结果传入，而是先执行完子查询再执行父查询，查询次数为 $m+n$ </p>
<h3 id="3-8-4-重复元组存在性测试（unique）"><a href="#3-8-4-重复元组存在性测试（unique）" class="headerlink" title="3.8.4 重复元组存在性测试（unique）"></a>3.8.4 重复元组存在性测试（unique）</h3><p><strong>unique</strong> 和 <strong>not unique</strong> 用于判断一个子查询的结果中是否存在重复的元组。<strong>unique</strong> 在其子句中的子查询中不包含重复元组时返回 <strong>true</strong>（==注：该结构尚未被广泛实现==）</p>
<p>考虑查询“找出在 $2017$ 年<strong>最多</strong>开设一次的所有课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> T.course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> course <span class="keyword">as</span> T</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> <span class="keyword">unique</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> R.course_id</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">from</span> section <span class="keyword">as</span> R</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">where</span> T.course_id<span class="operator">=</span> R.course_id <span class="keyword">and</span></span><br><span class="line">              R.year <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在不使用 <strong>unique</strong> 的情况下，上述查询的一种等价的表达方式为（注意为至多开设一次，一次都不开也是属于其中的）：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> T.course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> course <span class="keyword">as</span> T</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="operator">&gt;=</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">count</span>(R.course_id)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">from</span> section <span class="keyword">as</span> R</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">where</span> T.course_id<span class="operator">=</span> R.course_id <span class="keyword">and</span></span><br><span class="line">            R.year <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>not unique</strong> 可以用于测试一个子查询结果中是否存在重复元组，考虑查询“找出在 $2017$ 年至少开设两次的所有课程”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> T.course_id</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> course <span class="keyword">as</span> T</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">unique</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> R.course_id</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">from</span> section <span class="keyword">as</span> R</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">where</span> T.course_id<span class="operator">=</span> R.course_id <span class="keyword">and</span></span><br><span class="line">                  R.year <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2017</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-8-5-from-子句中的子查询"><a href="#3-8-5-from-子句中的子查询" class="headerlink" title="3.8.5 from 子句中的子查询"></a>3.8.5 from 子句中的子查询</h3><p>因为任何 <strong>select-from-where</strong> 表达式返回的结果都是关系，因此其应可以被插入到另一个 <strong>select-from-where</strong> 表达式中关系可以出现的任意位置</p>
<p>考虑查询“找出系平均工资超过 $42000$ 美元的那些系的教师的平均工资”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> dept name, avg salary</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> dept name, <span class="built_in">avg</span> (salary) <span class="keyword">as</span> avg salary</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> dept name)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> avg salary <span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="number">42000</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><a href="#having">此前</a>用过 <strong>having</strong> 子句来完成过该查询</p>
<h4 id="lateral-子句"><a href="#lateral-子句" class="headerlink" title="lateral 子句"></a>lateral 子句</h4><p>在 <strong>from</strong> 子句嵌套的子查询中不能使用来自同一 <strong>from</strong> 子句的其它关系的相关变量，若需要访问则需使用关键字 <strong>lateral</strong> 修饰子查询来进行该操作</p>
<p>考虑查询“每位教师的姓名，以及他们的工资中和他们所在系的平均工资”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> name, salary, avg salary</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> instructor I1, <span class="keyword">lateral</span> (<span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">avg</span>(salary) <span class="keyword">as</span> avg salary</span><br><span class="line">                             <span class="keyword">from</span> instructor I2</span><br><span class="line">                             <span class="keyword">where</span> I2.dept name<span class="operator">=</span> I1.dept name);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-8-6-with-子句"><a href="#3-8-6-with-子句" class="headerlink" title="3.8.6 with 子句"></a>3.8.6 with 子句</h3><p><strong>with</strong> 子句用于定义临时关系，这个关系只对包含 <strong>with</strong> 子句的查询有效，形式为：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>R<span class="operator">&gt;</span>(<span class="operator">&lt;</span>A1,A2,...<span class="operator">&gt;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span></span><br><span class="line">     (<span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>select_list<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     ...)<span class="comment">/*查询子句*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>select_list<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">...<span class="comment">/*查询语句*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>with</strong> 定义了一个临时关系 $R$，$R$ 后的属性 $A_1,A_2,\cdots$ 为定义的 $R$ 的属性，$R$ 的内容为子查询得到的内容，相当于通过引用 $R$ 及其属性 $A_i$ 来引用子查询中的内容</p>
<p>考虑查询“具有最大预算的那些系”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> max budget (<span class="keyword">value</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span></span><br><span class="line">     (<span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">max</span>(budget)</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> department)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> budget</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> department, max budget</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> department.budget <span class="operator">=</span> max budget.value;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>with</strong> 还可以同时定义多个临时关系，考虑查询“工资总额的大雨所有系平均工资总额的那些系”：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> dept total (dept name, <span class="keyword">value</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span></span><br><span class="line">     (<span class="keyword">select</span> dept name, <span class="built_in">sum</span>(salary)</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> instructor</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> dept name),</span><br><span class="line">     dept total <span class="built_in">avg</span>(<span class="keyword">value</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span></span><br><span class="line">     (<span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="built_in">avg</span>(<span class="keyword">value</span>)</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> dept total)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> dept name</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> dept total, dept total avg</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> dept total.value <span class="operator">&gt;</span> dept total avg.value;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>也可以用 <strong>from</strong> 和 <strong>where</strong> 的嵌套子查询完成上述查询要求，但相比之下会更加繁琐和不易读</p>
<h3 id="3-8-7-标量子查询"><a href="#3-8-7-标量子查询" class="headerlink" title="3.8.7 标量子查询"></a>3.8.7 标量子查询</h3><h3 id="3-8-8-不带-from-子句的标量"><a href="#3-8-8-不带-from-子句的标量" class="headerlink" title="3.8.8 不带 from 子句的标量"></a>3.8.8 不带 from 子句的标量</h3><h2 id="3-9-数据库的修改"><a href="#3-9-数据库的修改" class="headerlink" title="3.9 数据库的修改"></a>3.9 数据库的修改</h2><h3 id="3-9-1-删除"><a href="#3-9-1-删除" class="headerlink" title="3.9.1 删除"></a>3.9.1 删除</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">delete</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> R</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> P;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>即从关系 $R$ 中删除满足谓词 $P$ 的元组</p>
<h3 id="3-9-2-插入"><a href="#3-9-2-插入" class="headerlink" title="3.9.2 插入"></a>3.9.2 插入</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> R</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">values</span>(Data1, Data2, ...);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>$Data_i$ 从左到右分别对应关系 $R$ 从左到右的属性 $A_i$ </p>
<p>也可以指定数据将插入的对应的属性：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> R(A1, A2, ...)</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">values</span>(Data1, Data2, ...);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>也可以在查询的基础上插入元组</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> R</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">select</span> A1, A2, ...</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>tables<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">where</span> P</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>查询的结果必须要与 $R$ 中属性的类型相匹配</p>
<h3 id="3-9-3-更新"><a href="#3-9-3-更新" class="headerlink" title="3.9.3 更新"></a>3.9.3 更新</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">update R</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> <span class="operator">&lt;</span>expression<span class="operator">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> P</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>表示对关系 $R$ 中满足谓词 $P$ 的元组进行更新，set 子句中的表达式可以一般带有赋值语句</p>
<p>如将每位教师的工资涨 5%：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">update instructor</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> salary <span class="operator">=</span> salary <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="number">1.05</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> salary <span class="operator">&lt;</span> <span class="number">70000</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>表达式中可以使用 case 语句：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">when</span> pred1 <span class="keyword">then</span> result1 </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">when</span> pred2 <span class="keyword">then</span> result2 </span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">when</span> predn <span class="keyword">then</span> resultn</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> result0</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">update R</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> A <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">case</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">when</span> p1 <span class="keyword">then</span> r1</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">when</span> p2 <span class="keyword">then</span> r2</span><br><span class="line">	...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>相当于当 when 后的谓词 $pred_i$ 成立时，直接将 case 替换为 $result_i$</p>
<p>==注意：case 语句中 then 后不能使用表达式== </p>
